Uses of Package
io.github.pr0methean.betterrandom.util.spliterator

  • Packages that use io.github.pr0methean.betterrandom.util.spliterator 
    Package Description
    io.github.pr0methean.betterrandom.util.spliterator
    Implementations of Spliterator and unboxed-primitive equivalents that wrap a Supplier or the unboxed-primitive equivalent.
  • Classes in io.github.pr0methean.betterrandom.util.spliterator used by io.github.pr0methean.betterrandom.util.spliterator 
    Class and Description
    AbstractSupplierSpliterator
    An unordered, concurrent spliterator (possibly unboxed) that invokes a supplier (possibly unboxed) to get its values and has a preset size.
    DoubleSupplierSpliterator
    An unordered, concurrent Spliterator.OfDouble that invokes a DoubleSupplier to get its values and has a preset size.
    IntSupplierSpliterator
    An unordered, concurrent Spliterator.OfInt that invokes an IntSupplier to get its values and has a preset size.
    LongSupplierSpliterator
    An unordered, concurrent Spliterator.OfLong that invokes a LongSupplier to get its values and has a preset size.
